title: Women's Black Low Rise Baggy Jeans
description: These low rise, relaxed fit jeans feature straight leg style, slight distressed hem detailing, silver button closure & zip at front, belt loops, 5 pocket design. Pair with a cute crop top and sneakers for a casual but chic look.
True to size,Model is a Size XS & is wearing a Size XS.
Style them with a cute baby tee and some chunky sneakers for the ultimate IT girl fit!
Machine wash at maximum of 30oC, do not bleach, tumble dry low, iron at a maximum of 110oC, do not dry clean.
